CORE ARCHITECTURAL DOCUMENTATION
================================

This directory contains the 15-part foundational documentation series for AWCMS-Micro.

PURPOSE:
To define the architectural authority, governance standards, and implementation roadmap for the platform, ensuring full compatibility with the EmDash CMS upstream.

CORE TOPICS:
- Part 1-3: Foundation (Architecture, Ops, Storage)
- Part 4-5: Logic (Plugins, ABAC)
- Part 6-8: Delivery (Frontend, Security, Cloudflare)
- Part 9-11: Implementation (Sprint Plan, Website/School Templates)
- Part 12-13: Expansion (Mobile SDK, ERP-Ready)
- Part 14-15: Maintenance (Upstream Sync, Master Index)

These documents serve as the Source of Truth for all AWCMS-Micro development.
